threads.title: 820-00875 dead cpu??
threads.message:
All other  power rails are present except ppvccgt_s0g_ph3, ph1ph2 and ppvcccpu_s0g_ph1, ph2.
i have removed l7210,l7220, l7410,l7420and l7430 and diode mode measurement on cpu side is 0.002 and 0.000.
is it dead cpu?

threads.title: 820-00875 dead cpu??
threads.message: Very likely yes. I'm guessing DC in is 20 volts and PPBUS is 13? If so, yeah this is probably trash.

threads.title: 820-00875 dead cpu??
threads.message: I haven't measured dcin, but ppbus is definitely 13 volts

threads.title: 820-00875 dead cpu??
threads.message: Yeah if it's 13 then DC in has to be 20. This is probably dead.
